com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.snomedrefset

Interface SnomedModuleDependencyRefSetMember

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject, org.eclipse.emf.cdo.common.id.CDOWithID, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SnomedRefSetMember
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Rf2RefSetMember, SnomedModuleDependencyRefSetMemberImpl, UnsupportedRf2RefSetMember

    public interface SnomedModuleDependencyRefSetMember
extends SnomedRefSetMember
    Represents a SNOMED CT module dependency reference set member.

    The following features are supported:

    • Source Effective Time
    • Target Effective Time

    See Also:
    SnomedRefSetPackage.getSnomedModuleDependencyRefSetMember()
